snippet.title: SnapDragon gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for SnapDragon, Dos PC game produced by MECC in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/snapdragon/12765/
SnapDragon is an educational game. The player is helping the SnapDragon to complete his photo album.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
